                  <summary><p>A composite manuscript, entitled <title xml:lang="ta">caritttirama Iraṇṭu</title> on its additional <locus facs="3">title page</locus>, containing:
  <list rend="numbered">
    <item>The <title xml:lang="ta">Maturai Vīraṉ Katai</title> (Indien 428a).</item>
    <item>The <title xml:lang="ta">Tēr Ūrnta Cōḻaṉ Carittiram</title> (Indien 428b).</item></list>
</p>
<p>There are 2 additional title pages in the bundle: one for the whole bundle (Indien 428, U1) and one for the second work (Indien 428b, U1). A deprecated title page, unblackened and partially deleted, has been used as back guard leaf (Indien 428, U2).</p>
   <p>Description based on the digital images available on Gallica.</p>      </summary>
                  
